~ start
if GlobalState.PaidKyle:
	Kyle: [[Sup Bro!|Thanks for my money.|Hi|Hello|Howdy]]
else:
	Kyle: [[Remember you still owe me.|Where's my money?|Let me get my money.|You got my money?]]
	if GlobalState.game.money >= 125:
		Me: [[Here!|I got it.|Right away boss.]]
		do GlobalState.game.money -= 125
		Kyle: [[Good kid!|See you around|You better.]]
		set GlobalState.PaidKyle = true
	else:
		Me: [[I'll get your $125 soon!|It's just $125!|Okay! Okay! I'll bring your $125]]
=> END